### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Swagger UI
GET http://localhost:3000/api-docs


### USERS — autenticación y perfil

### 1. Registrar usuario (devuelve accessToken y refreshToken)
POST {{base}}/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@bildyapp.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}

### 2. Login
POST {{base}}/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@bildyapp.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}

### 3. Renovar token (usa @refreshToken)
POST {{base}}/user/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### 4. Verificar email con código recibido
PUT {{base}}/user/validation
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "{{verifyCode}}"
}

### 5. Actualizar datos personales
PUT {{base}}/user/register
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Demo",
  "lastName": "User",
  "nif": "12345678A"
}

### 6. Crear / unirse a empresa
PATCH {{base}}/user/company
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Construcciones Demo SL",
  "cif": "B12345678",
  "address": {
    "street": "Calle Mayor",
    "number": "10",
    "postal": "28001",
    "city": "Madrid",
    "province": "Madrid"
  }
}

### 6b. Empresa como autónomo (isFreelance)
PATCH {{base}}/user/company
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isFreelance": true
}

### 7. Subir logo de empresa (multipart)
PATCH {{base}}/user/logo
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="logo"; filename="logo.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./logo.png
--boundary--

### 8. Obtener perfil propio (con empresa populada)
GET {{base}}/user
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Cambiar contraseña
PUT {{base}}/user/password
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "Password123",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword456"
}

### 10. Invitar usuario a la empresa (solo admin)
POST {{base}}/user/invite
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{guestEmail}}",
  "name": "Guest",
  "lastName": "User",
  "password": "{{guestPassword}}"
}

### 11. Logout (invalida refreshToken)
POST {{base}}/user/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Eliminar cuenta — soft (archiva)
DELETE {{base}}/user?soft=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12b. Eliminar cuenta — hard (permanente)
DELETE {{base}}/user
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### CLIENTS

### 13. Crear cliente
POST {{base}}/client
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Construcciones García SA",
  "cif": "A87654321",
  "email": "info@garcia.com",
  "phone": "+34600000001",
  "address": {
    "street": "Gran Vía",
    "number": "1",
    "postal": "28013",
    "city": "Madrid",
    "province": "Madrid"
  }
}

### 14. Listar clientes (paginado)
GET {{base}}/client?page=1&limit=10&sort=-createdAt
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 14b. Filtrar clientes por nombre
GET {{base}}/client?name=García&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 15. Obtener cliente por ID
GET {{base}}/client/{{clientId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 16. Actualizar cliente
PUT {{base}}/client/{{clientId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "+34611111111",
  "email": "nuevo@garcia.com"
}

### 17. Archivar cliente (soft delete)
DELETE {{base}}/client/{{clientId}}?soft=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 17b. Eliminar cliente permanentemente
DELETE {{base}}/client/{{clientId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 18. Listar clientes archivados
GET {{base}}/client/archived?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 19. Restaurar cliente archivado
PATCH {{base}}/client/{{clientId}}/restore
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### PROJECTS

### 20. Crear proyecto
POST {{base}}/project
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Reforma Oficinas Centro",
  "projectCode": "PRJ-2025-001",
  "client": "{{clientId}}",
  "address": {
    "street": "Gran Vía",
    "number": "1",
    "postal": "28013",
    "city": "Madrid",
    "province": "Madrid"
  },
  "email": "obra@garcia.com",
  "notes": "Acceso por puerta trasera",
  "active": true
}

### 21. Listar proyectos activos (paginado)
GET {{base}}/project?page=1&limit=10&active=true&sort=-createdAt
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 21b. Filtrar proyectos por cliente
GET {{base}}/project?client={{clientId}}&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 21c. Filtrar proyectos por nombre
GET {{base}}/project?name=Reforma&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 22. Obtener proyecto por ID
GET {{base}}/project/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 23. Actualizar proyecto
PUT {{base}}/project/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notes": "Acceso actualizado — puerta principal",
  "active": false
}

### 24. Archivar proyecto (soft delete)
DELETE {{base}}/project/{{projectId}}?soft=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 24b. Eliminar proyecto permanentemente
DELETE {{base}}/project/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 25. Listar proyectos archivados
GET {{base}}/project/archived?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 26. Restaurar proyecto archivado
PATCH {{base}}/project/{{projectId}}/restore
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### DELIVERY NOTES — albaranes

### 27. Crear albarán de horas (workers)
POST {{base}}/deliverynote
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "project": "{{projectId}}",
  "client": "{{clientId}}",
  "format": "hours",
  "description": "Jornada de pintura interior",
  "workDate": "2025-06-15",
  "workers": [
    { "name": "Carlos López", "hours": 8 },
    { "name": "Ana Martínez", "hours": 6 }
  ]
}

### 27b. Crear albarán de horas (total sin workers)
POST {{base}}/deliverynote
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "project": "{{projectId}}",
  "client": "{{clientId}}",
  "format": "hours",
  "description": "Jornada de replanteo",
  "workDate": "2025-06-16",
  "hours": 4
}

### 28. Crear albarán de materiales
POST {{base}}/deliverynote
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "project": "{{projectId}}",
  "client": "{{clientId}}",
  "format": "material",
  "description": "Suministro cemento",
  "workDate": "2025-06-15",
  "material": "Cemento Portland",
  "quantity": 500,
  "unit": "kg"
}

### 29. Listar albaranes (paginado)
GET {{base}}/deliverynote?page=1&limit=10&sort=-workDate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 29b. Filtrar por proyecto
GET {{base}}/deliverynote?project={{projectId}}&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 29c. Filtrar por cliente
GET {{base}}/deliverynote?client={{clientId}}&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 29d. Filtrar por formato
GET {{base}}/deliverynote?format=hours&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 29e. Filtrar no firmados
GET {{base}}/deliverynote?signed=false&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 29f. Filtrar por rango de fechas
GET {{base}}/deliverynote?from=2025-01-01&to=2025-12-31&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 30. Obtener albarán por ID (con relaciones populadas)
GET {{base}}/deliverynote/{{noteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 31. Descargar PDF del albarán
GET {{base}}/deliverynote/pdf/{{noteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 32. Firmar albarán (sube imagen de firma — multipart)
PATCH {{base}}/deliverynote/{{noteId}}/sign
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="signature"; filename="firma.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpg

< ./firma.jpg
--boundary--

### 33. Eliminar albarán (solo si no está firmado)
DELETE {{base}}/deliverynote/{{noteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
